  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I will continue to serve my motherland - former President Kota assured",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has said that he will continue to serve the motherland after resigning from the presidency.",
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa mentioned this in his resignation letter which was read today in Parliament.",
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Thammika Dasanayake read the resignation letter sent to the Speaker when the Parliament met today.",
        "In that letter, within 3 months of my inauguration as President, the Covid-19 pandemic had affected the entire world.",
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa expressed his satisfaction with the efforts made to protect Sri Lanka from the pandemic at that time.",
        "In his resignation letter, he noted that the implementation of the lockdowns in 2020 and 2021 has caused the country to lose foreign exchange and continue to hurt an already battered economy.",
        "I called on all parties in Parliament to form an all-party government to address this volatile economy."
      ],
